{"tid":1632191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[公投] 黎緊幾日勇武定和理","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T03:34:25.000Z","uid":331469,"like":14,"dislike":89,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"1407f6acb4d14d4bda5e8847c393b7314a76b851","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"因為我係p牌仔，我唔會係2個選擇有立場。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇左好多post, <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 1.有人認為黎緊幾日用勇武(18區開花，裝修) </span>; <span style=\"color: blue;\">2.有人覺得黎緊幾日係要和理主場，勇武暫時休息 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n兩方都各有原因同利弊，所以下我會列出暫時見到既兩方好壞 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意：決定會左右成場運動結果，請慎重選擇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.勇武繼續</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好：</span></span><br />\n-話比港共知反蒙面法係唔會令到我地驚<br />\n-港共暫時冇棋可以止暴制亂<br />\n-繼續打壓紅黑色企業<br />\n-話比港共知反蒙面法係唔會令到我地驚<br />\n-港共暫時冇棋可以止暴制亂<br />\n-繼續打壓紅黑色企業<br />\n-間接制做3罷(empty R)，經濟跌，向攬炒邁進<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">壞：</span></span><br />\n-國際輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-令人權法案有阻礙(甚至過唔到)<br />\n-民生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-總有中立 淺黃反感<br />\n-更多手足受傷，被捕(要視乎抗爭模式)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.和理上場，勇武休息</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好：</span></span><br />\n-國際輿論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-唔會為人權法案制造阻礙<br />\n-話比政府知和勇不割<br />\n-民生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-勇武可以有休息時間<br />\n-紅黑企業商鋪有修復時間，下次大型裝修成效更大<br />\n-減少手足流血，被捕<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">壞：</span></span><br />\n-間接同港共/洗共以為 反蒙面法有阻嚇力/成效<br />\n-為警方增加清算時間<br />\n-為政府提供更多計策時間<br />\n-市民抗爭既火會冷卻(總有人會)<br />\n-增加勇武手足再行動的阻礙(比時間警方計劃行動)<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">-有機會有鬼繼續扮勇武4圍放火破壞</span><br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多，以下公投決定黎緊幾日運動去向：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />繼續勇武<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />和理上場，勇武暫休"},{"pid":"f74c9347ff403236db7d757a1b945e64163b9a0e","tid":1632191,"uid":12970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:12:48.000Z","msg":"獨立思考<br />\n行動必需目標明確<br />\n不要被仇恨支配<br />\n聆聽他人意見<br />\n但不要盲目跟從<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"157d6169488d67ca687add4b3f71f481f48666ee","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:13:26.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"34127ae42895809dac9777599def59b471230029","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:13:43.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"36fa7188b6733377997fc2b3b62a4f91f1f508dd","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:14:00.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"eb976556ddac3ea5e5567f49885486419c96dc90","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:15:22.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"c852a7dd6910027839f528994b3ebb1612569344","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:15:32.000Z","msg":"uppp"},{"pid":"84db17910dd8253ba5748392c9b37a1fb004ba3a","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:16:15.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"fab776aae359933f4976b06a579c6a45a3653be9","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:17:07.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"828e0978133516318ab64916793e364791c27423","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:19:41.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"dc28350a0a1534e64c537c65d58211fd3e64016e","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:29.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"f815d34045b86d4a4b8d5ac1a27888520ec9eb69","tid":1632191,"uid":237645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:12.000Z","msg":"跪求大家 其他事唔好再討論😪<br />\n<br />\n1）呢一星期全民文宣 做翻6月果時文宣既陣容/級數<br />\n🚨主力國際線🚨<br />\n<br />\n識整文宣既主力整文宣<br />\nEtc 警暴濫權 政府暴政 送中條例 緊急法<br />\n英文人上場 盡量翻譯警暴同緊急法文宣<br />\n<br />\n唔識整既就善用media linkage瘋狂Share<br />\n<br />\n2）全民down twitter同reddit<br />\n岀post等外國人知道香港最新情況<br />\n好多外媒其實能力有限 覆蓋率唔高<br />\n和理非英文人多啲翻譯中文文宣<br />\n<br />\n手動轉去各大group"},{"pid":"ff84585dde69800d652a5d53008d22758e6dab94","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"push 大家有唔同意見"},{"pid":"95a9558ba4d19507716a4c87f902e07acf29e02c","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:29.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"cea409a5bbfa6dfc39e0a28e21ab1975e243dffb","tid":1632191,"uid":235024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:34.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6457bb23fec7e37d4f0ee4ef9b5c9e1a438620a6","tid":1632191,"uid":331469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:18.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"516f37b89a1d0b4fff37fd01a29f434d989ff6e3","tid":1632191,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[18區開花] 一句講晒，聽日一點定八點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"50d60943dd5e49c1040a8a7acefc712bbb69118f","tid":1632191,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:20.000Z","msg":"點解一定要輪流，一齊出場，各自努力唔得咩"},{"pid":"fdd4718c330b50700b830fb82107ef29296905cf","tid":1632191,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:34:23.000Z","msg":"有建設做緊既話，而裝修幫到三罷，咁可能輿論會正面少少"},{"pid":"0263b46d4fbd8db26c06333f256fba1e6171bfd5","tid":1632191,"uid":31341,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"50d60943dd5e49c1040a8a7acefc712bbb69118f","tid":1632191,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:20.000Z","msg":"點解一定要輪流，一齊出場，各自努力唔得咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:38:05.000Z","msg":"今日吹行雞話要和平遊行 結果都係損失慘重"},{"pid":"8fb3e966d11ade694a81c376f9f3c10f11a1b31d","tid":1632191,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:38:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"d439573a4f119a24b186e4bc8286bf8a488d109e","tid":1632191,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:42:31.000Z","msg":"和理轉主攻，勇武各區快閃"},{"pid":"2b10cbc8aae854a04c609eddf1e8f8f9a72c8f71","tid":1632191,"uid":266051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:43:48.000Z","msg":"又問呢條？不如你答左我18區定1區先啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yt2LiQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYt2LiQM.jpg&h=78ad1817&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e69663968f986b6deb3183922f80440cdd0120c","tid":1632191,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:07:08.000Z","msg":"其實就算做和理活動都可以戴口罩<br />\n表現到我地唔驚佢條緊急法。"},{"pid":"d43056a9ac2542d8bb6c4a8b0a4e5fddb58eaa9d","tid":1632191,"uid":111907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:09:22.000Z","msg":"［核彈整合，文宣組入黎］衝衝子辛苦晒，跟住落黎呢幾日係文宣回合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632398\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632398</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dee7ce41eff0fd93e4a5f171767d0610d4751b59","tid":1632191,"uid":101623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50d60943dd5e49c1040a8a7acefc712bbb69118f","tid":1632191,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:20.000Z","msg":"點解一定要輪流，一齊出場，各自努力唔得咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:09:35.000Z","msg":"某程度上唔得<br />\n勇武一岀就會spin晒focus落勇武到"},{"pid":"e06c6e5eccd544188412ad3f60e9c87186232f2f","tid":1632191,"uid":38737,"like":0,"disli